node.text:
FORUM 84 ADV by Diego Nájera /// Available now in select skate shops and online at adidas.com/skateboarding

Playing with mixed materials across the shoe, including translucent elements and layered white tones the shoe nods back to Diego’s passion for import car culture. The result is easy on the eyes with levels of complexity for those who appreciate the details.

Features: •Full grain leather panels •Suede eyestay •Mesh textile backed stripes •Tumbled leather toe box •Transparent TPU clip •Removable velcro strap •Ice blue transparent outsole which features Diego’s signature underneath.
•
#adidasSkateboarding #adidasForum
